      "type": "text-only",
      "settings": {
        "large_text": "",
        "small_text": "<p>Founder of Crafter's Companion, Sara Davies joined forces with Vicky Pattison, Alex Scott & Laura Whitmore to take on the Arctic for Comic Relief 2024. The team of four took on gruelling conditions and plummeting temperatures to complete the trek in aid of tackling poverty around the world. <\/p><p>To read more about Sara's experience and discover why this charity is so close to her heart head on over to <a href=\"https:\/\/sara-davies.com\/on-tv\/comic-relief\/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/sara-davies.com\/on-tv\/comic-relief\/\">Sara Davies<\/a> website.<\/p>",
